    <h2>Can anybody read what I wrote?</h2>

    <p>No, all your writing will be private and not submitted to or stored on any server.</p>

    <h2 id="nanowrimo">What's the deal with #NaNoWriMo?</h2>

    <p>The <a href="http://nanowrimo.org" title="National Novel Writing Month">National Novel Writing Month</a> is an annual challange for writers to write the first draft of a novel from scratch to finish in November. </p>


    <p>If you want to support your NaNoWriMo friends and <i class="icon-mdwa"></i> <abbr title="The Most Dangerous Writing App">MDWA</abbr>, please spread the love on twitter:</p>

    <a id="tweet" class="dark narrow" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=I+used+the+Most+Dangerous+Writing+App+for+my+#NaNoWriMo+novel+today!+#MDWA&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.themostdangerouswritingapp.com" target="_blank">I used the Most Dangerous Writing App for my #NaNoWriMo novel today!</a>

    <p>Since I believe in eating my own dog food, I am writing an entire novel using this app; one thousand six hundred and sixty-seven words a day in a single run. It is the fourth scariest thing I ever did.</p>

    <p>If you dare, you can join me:</p>
